<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Le Passé Simple — Gramática francesa B2+</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #ede9df;
  --card: #faf7f1;
  --border: #c4bead;
  --text: #1a1814;
  --text2: #44413a;
  --text3: #706c64;
  --accent: #7a5a0a;
  --accent-light: #f0e0c0;
  --accent-mid: #b89050;
  --warn-bg: #fdf0cc;
  --shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.11), 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --radius: 14px;
  --radius-sm: 8px;
  --green: #1a6028;   --green-bg: #e4f2e8;
  --red: #a81e2e;     --red-bg: #fce6e8;
  --blue: #163494;    --blue-bg: #e6ebf8;
  --purple: #6a1a8a;  --purple-bg: #f2e6f8;
  --ps-color: #8a1a2e;
  --ps-bg: #f8e6ea;
  --fs: 15px;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; }

html, body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: var(--fs);
  line-height: 1.55;
}

h1, h2, h3, h4 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  color: var(--text);
  margin: 0 0 0.4em 0;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

p { margin: 0.6em 0; }

a { color: var(--accent); }

/* ----------- HEADER ----------- */
.site-header {
  background: var(--card);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 28px 24px 22px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.header-top {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 14px;
}
.header-top h1 {
  font-size: 2.4em;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: italic;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--text);
}
.header-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  background: var(--accent-light);
  color: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.78em;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.subtitle {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 6px auto 0;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 1.05em;
  font-style: italic;
}
.stats-row {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 18px auto 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  align-items: center;
}
.stat-pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 5px 12px;
  background: var(--accent-light);
  color: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.85em;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.stat-pill.ps {
  background: var(--ps-bg);
  color: var(--ps-color);
}
.fs-wrap {
  margin-left: auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 0.85em;
  color: var(--text3);
}
.fs-wrap input[type=range] {
  width: 100px;
  accent-color: var(--accent);
}

/* ----------- SECTION NAV ----------- */
.section-nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  background: var(--bg);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  z-index: 100;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}
.section-nav-inner {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  gap: 4px;
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}
.snav-btn {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 0.86em;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--text3);
  cursor: pointer;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  white-space: nowrap;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.15s ease;
}
.snav-btn:hover { color: var(--text2); background: var(--card); }
.snav-btn.active {
  color: var(--accent);
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ----------- MAIN LAYOUT ----------- */
.main-layout {
  max-width: 860px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 28px 20px 80px;
}

.sec-block { display: none; }
.sec-block.active { display: block; }

.sec-block > h2 {
  font-size: 1.9em;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 0 0 22px 0;
  color: var(--text);
  letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}

.sec-label {
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 0.74em;
  letter-spacing: 1.2px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin: 26px 0 10px;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
}

/* ----------- CARDS ----------- */
.gram-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  margin-bottom: 22px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.gram-card-body {
  padding: 22px 24px;
}

.def-box {
  background: var(--warn-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  margin: 12px 0 18px;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.98em;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.def-box strong { color: var(--text); }

.warn-box {
  background: var(--red-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--red);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  margin: 14px 0;
  color: var(--text2);
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  font-size: 0.95em;
}
.warn-box::before {
  content: "⚠️";
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-size: 1.05em;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
.warn-text { flex: 1; }

.note-box {
  background: var(--purple-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--purple);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  margin: 14px 0;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.94em;
}
.note-box strong { color: var(--text); }

/* ----------- EXAMPLES ----------- */
.example-block {
  background: var(--blue-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  margin: 10px 0;
}
.example-block.ps {
  background: var(--ps-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--ps-color);
}
.example-block.neu {
  background: var(--blue-bg);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
}
.example-block.mix {
  background: var(--card);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--text);
}
.ex-fr {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 1.04em;
}
.ex-fr .eps {
  color: var(--ps-color);
  font-weight: 700;
}
.ex-es {
  font-size: 0.92em;
  color: var(--text2);
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.ex-note {
  font-size: 0.82em;
  color: var(--text3);
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ----------- CHIPS ----------- */
.chip-bar {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
  margin: 14px 0 14px;
  padding-bottom: 4px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.chip {
  background: var(--bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text2);
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 0.86em;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 6px 13px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s ease;
}
.chip:hover { background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--accent); }
.chip.active {
  background: var(--ps-color);
  color: white;
  border-color: var(--ps-color);
  font-weight: 600;
}
.chip-panel { display: none; }
.chip-panel.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.2s ease; }

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(2px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* ----------- TABLES ----------- */
.table-wrap {
  overflow-x: auto;
  margin: 14px 0;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.gram-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 0.93em;
  background: var(--card);
}
.gram-table th, .gram-table td {
  padding: 9px 12px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.gram-table th {
  background: var(--accent-light);
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.82em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.4px;
}
.gram-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.gram-table .hl-ps { color: var(--ps-color); font-weight: 700; }
.gram-table .hl { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
.gram-table .dim { color: var(--text3); }

/* ----------- CONJ TABLE ----------- */
.conj-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 0.95em;
  background: var(--card);
}
.conj-table th, .conj-table td {
  padding: 8px 12px;
  text-align: left;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.conj-table .conj-pron {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text3);
  width: 40%;
}
.conj-table .conj-form-ps {
  color: var(--ps-color);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 1.05em;
}
.conj-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

/* ----------- TRAPS ----------- */
.trap-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  padding: 16px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.trap-card-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.trap-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 1.08em;
}
.trap-vs {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  margin: 8px 0 8px;
}
.trap-wrong, .trap-right {
  padding: 7px 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 0.96em;
}
.trap-wrong {
  background: var(--red-bg);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  color: var(--red);
}
.trap-wrong::before { content: "✗ "; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; }
.trap-right {
  background: var(--green-bg);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
  color: var(--green);
}
.trap-right::before { content: "✓ "; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; }
.trap-expl {
  margin-top: 8px;
  color: var(--text2);
  font-size: 0.92em;
  line-height: 1.55;
}

/* ----------- TIMELINE ----------- */
.timeline {
  margin: 18px 0;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}
.tl-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 8px 0;
  align-items: flex-start;
  border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
}
.tl-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.tl-item::before {
  content: "";
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  margin-top: 6px;
  background: var(--text3);
}
.tl-item.ps::before { background: var(--ps-color); }
.tl-item.pc::before { background: var(--blue); }
.tl-item.now::before { background: var(--green); }
.tl-item.pqp::before { background: var(--purple); }
.tl-item-body {
  flex: 1;
  font-size: 0.94em;
  color: var(--text2);
}
.tl-item-body strong { color: var(--text); }

/* ----------- LEGEND ----------- */
.legend-row {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin: 12px 0 14px;
}
.legend-pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.83em;
  font-weight: 600;
  background: var(--accent-light);
  color: var(--accent);
}
.legend-pill.ps {
  background: var(--ps-bg);
  color: var(--ps-color);
}

/* ----------- RESPONSIVE ----------- */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .site-header { padding: 22px 16px 18px; }
  .header-top h1 { font-size: 1.8em; }
  .main-layout { padding: 20px 14px 60px; }
  .gram-card-body { padding: 18px 16px; }
  .sec-block > h2 { font-size: 1.5em; }
  .fs-wrap { width: 100%; margin-left: 0; margin-top: 8px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-top">
    <h1>Le Passé Simple</h1>
    <span class="header-tag">Grammaire</span>
  </div>
  <div class="subtitle">Gramática francesa · DALF C1 / Avanzado B2+</div>
  <div class="stats-row">
    <span class="stat-pill ps">Passé simple</span>
    <span class="stat-pill">Temps littéraire</span>
    <span class="stat-pill">Registre soutenu</span>
    <div class="fs-wrap">
      <span>A</span>
      <input type="range" min="13" max="20" value="15" oninput="setFontSize(this.value)">
      <span style="font-size:1.15em">A</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<nav class="section-nav">
  <div class="section-nav-inner">
    <button class="snav-btn active" onclick="showSection('sec1', this)">1. Visión general</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec2', this)">2. Formación · 1.er grupo</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec3', this)">3. Formación · 2.º y 3.er grupo</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec4', this)">4. Irregulares</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec5', this)">5. Usos y contextos</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec6', this)">6. PS vs. PC</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec7', this)">7. PS en subordinadas</button>
    <button class="snav-btn" onclick="showSection('sec8', this)">8. Trampas</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="main-layout">

<!-- =================== SECTION 1 =================== -->
<section id="sec1" class="sec-block active">
  <h2>1. Visión general</h2>

  <div class="gram-card">
    <div class="gram-card-body">
      <div class="def-box">
        El passé simple (también llamado <em>passé défini</em> o <em>passé historique</em>) es un tiempo verbal del <strong>modo indicativo</strong> que expresa acciones <strong>puntuales, completadas y delimitadas</strong> en el pasado. En el francés moderno es un tiempo <strong>exclusivamente escrito y de registro elevado</strong> (literario, histórico, periodístico formal). En la lengua oral ha sido reemplazado completamente por el passé composé.
      </div>

      <div class="legend-row">
        <span class="legend-pill ps">Passé simple — acción puntual en lengua escrita / literaria</span>
      </div>

      <div class="sec-label">Eje temporal</div>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="tl-item ps">
          <div class="tl-item-body">
            <strong>Passé simple</strong> — acción puntual y completa, en el pasado.<br>
            <em>Le roi <span style="color:var(--ps-color);font-weight:700">mourut</span> en 1715.</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item pc">
          <div class="tl-item-body">
            <strong>Passé composé</strong> — equivalente oral/informal del PS.<br>
            <em>Le roi est mort.</em>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item now">
          <div class="tl-item-body">
            <strong>Présent</strong> — punto de referencia del lector/narrador.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warn-box">
        <div class="warn-text">
          El passé simple <strong>NO se usa en conversación oral, ni en cartas informales, ni en mensajes</strong>. Usarlo en una conversación resulta pedante o cómico. En el habla, siempre se sustituye por el <strong>passé composé</strong>.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sec-label">PS vs. PC — comparación rápida</div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table class="gram-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Criterio</th><th>Passé simple</th><th>Passé composé</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Registro</td><td>Escrito, literario, formal</td><td>Oral, escrito informal</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Relación con el presente</td><td>Acción totalmente separada del presente</td><td>Puede tener vínculo con el presente</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Auxiliar</td><td>No lleva auxiliar (forma sintética)</td><td><em>avoir / être</em> + participio</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Uso típico</td><td>Novelas, historia, prensa formal</td><td>Conversación, cartas, blog</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Personas más frecuentes</td><td>3.ª sg. y pl. (<em>il, elle, ils, elles</em>)</td><td>Todas</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="note-box">
        En textos literarios y periodísticos, las 1.ª y 2.ª personas del PS (<em>je, tu, nous, vous</em>) aparecen, pero son menos frecuentes. En la narrativa en 3.ª persona, <em>il/elle/ils/elles</em> dominan absolutamente.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- =================== SECTION 2 =================== -->
<section id="sec2" class="sec-block">
  <h2>2. Formación — 1.er grupo (-ER)</h2>

  <div class="gram-card">
    <div class="gram-card-body">
      <div class="def-box">
        Los verbos del 1.er grupo (-ER) y el verbo <strong>aller</strong> forman el PS con las terminaciones <strong>-ai, -as, -a, -âmes, -âtes, -èrent</strong>. La raíz es el infinitivo sin -ER.
      </div>

      <div class="chip-bar">
        <button class="chip active" onclick="selectChip('grp1', 0, this)">PARLER</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp1', 1, this)">AIMER</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp1', 2, this)">ALLER</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp1', 3, this)">Verbos -CER / -GER</button>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel active" data-group="grp1" data-idx="0">
        <div class="sec-label">PARLER — passé simple</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">je</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parlai</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parlas</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parla</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parlâmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parlâtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">parlèrent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp1" data-idx="1">
        <div class="sec-label">AIMER — passé simple</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">j'</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aimai</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aimas</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aima</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aimâmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aimâtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">aimèrent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp1" data-idx="2">
        <div class="sec-label">ALLER — passé simple</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.92em;color:var(--text3);margin-top:4px"><em>Irregular en otros tiempos, pero sigue las terminaciones regulares de -ER en passé simple.</em></p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">j'</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allai</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allas</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">alla</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allâmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allâtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allèrent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp1" data-idx="3">
        <div class="sec-label">Verbos en -CER y -GER</div>
        <p><strong>-CER</strong>: la <em>c</em> recibe cédille ante -a para conservar el sonido [s] → <em>commencer → il <span class="hl-ps">commença</span></em>.</p>
        <p><strong>-GER</strong>: conservan la <em>-e-</em> ante -a para mantener el sonido [ʒ] → <em>manger → il <span class="hl-ps">mangea</span></em>.</p>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="gram-table">
            <thead>
              <tr><th>Infinitivo</th><th>il / elle</th><th>ils / elles</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>commencer</td><td class="hl-ps">commença</td><td class="hl-ps">commencèrent</td></tr>
              <tr><td>avancer</td><td class="hl-ps">avança</td><td class="hl-ps">avancèrent</td></tr>
              <tr><td>manger</td><td class="hl-ps">mangea</td><td class="hl-ps">mangèrent</td></tr>
              <tr><td>nager</td><td class="hl-ps">nagea</td><td class="hl-ps">nagèrent</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warn-box">
        <div class="warn-text">
          La terminación de <em>nous</em> (<strong>-âmes</strong>) y <em>vous</em> (<strong>-âtes</strong>) lleva <strong>acento circunflejo</strong> sobre la â. Es un error frecuente omitirlo. La ortografía correcta es: <em>nous parlâmes</em>, <em>vous parlâtes</em>.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sec-label">Ejemplos</div>
      <div class="example-block ps">
        <div class="ex-fr">Il <span class="eps">parla</span> longuement de son enfance.</div>
        <div class="ex-es">Habló largamente de su infancia.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="example-block ps">
        <div class="ex-fr">Elle <span class="eps">aima</span> cet homme toute sa vie.</div>
        <div class="ex-es">Amó a ese hombre toda su vida.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="example-block ps">
        <div class="ex-fr">Ils <span class="eps">allèrent</span> à Paris pour la première fois.</div>
        <div class="ex-es">Fueron a París por primera vez.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="example-block ps">
        <div class="ex-fr">Le navire <span class="eps">s'approcha</span> du port à l'aube.</div>
        <div class="ex-es">El barco se acercó al puerto al amanecer.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- =================== SECTION 3 =================== -->
<section id="sec3" class="sec-block">
  <h2>3. Formación — 2.º y 3.er grupo</h2>

  <div class="gram-card">
    <div class="gram-card-body">
      <div class="def-box">
        Los verbos del 2.º grupo (-IR tipo <em>finir</em>) y la mayoría del 3.er grupo (-IR, -RE, -OIR) siguen dos patrones principales de terminaciones en PS: el de <strong>-is / -it / -irent</strong> y el de <strong>-us / -ut / -urent</strong>.
      </div>

      <div class="chip-bar">
        <button class="chip active" onclick="selectChip('grp23', 0, this)">2.º grupo (-IR)</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp23', 1, this)">3.er grupo · -is</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp23', 2, this)">3.er grupo · -us</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('grp23', 3, this)">Formas en -int</button>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel active" data-group="grp23" data-idx="0">
        <div class="sec-label">2.º grupo — FINIR</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">je</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finis</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finis</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finit</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finîmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finîtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">finirent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="note-box">
          <strong>Attention</strong> — en presente: <em>il finit</em> (con t final) = passé simple <em>il finit</em> (idénticos en escritura). Solo el contexto diferencia.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp23" data-idx="1">
        <div class="sec-label">Verbos del 3.er grupo con raíz en -IS-</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="gram-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Infinitivo</th><th>3.ª sg.</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>prendre</td><td class="hl-ps">prit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>mettre</td><td class="hl-ps">mit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>dire</td><td class="hl-ps">dit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>écrire</td><td class="hl-ps">écrivit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>faire</td><td class="hl-ps">fit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>rire</td><td class="hl-ps">rit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>conduire</td><td class="hl-ps">conduisit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>naître</td><td class="hl-ps">naquit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>asseoir</td><td class="hl-ps">assit</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="sec-label">PRENDRE — paradigma completo</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">je</td><td class="conj-form-ps">pris</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">pris</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">prit</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">prîmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">prîtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">prirent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp23" data-idx="2">
        <div class="sec-label">Verbos del 3.er grupo con raíz en -US-</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="gram-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Infinitivo</th><th>3.ª sg.</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>avoir</td><td class="hl-ps">eut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>boire</td><td class="hl-ps">but</td></tr>
              <tr><td>connaître</td><td class="hl-ps">connut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>courir</td><td class="hl-ps">courut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>croire</td><td class="hl-ps">crut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>devoir</td><td class="hl-ps">dut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>falloir</td><td class="hl-ps">fallut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>lire</td><td class="hl-ps">lut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>mourir</td><td class="hl-ps">mourut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>plaire</td><td class="hl-ps">plut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>pleuvoir</td><td class="hl-ps">plut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>pouvoir</td><td class="hl-ps">put</td></tr>
              <tr><td>recevoir</td><td class="hl-ps">reçut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>savoir</td><td class="hl-ps">sut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>tenir <span class="dim">(excepción)</span></td><td class="hl-ps">tint</td></tr>
              <tr><td>valoir</td><td class="hl-ps">valut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>vivre</td><td class="hl-ps">vécut</td></tr>
              <tr><td>voir <span class="dim">(excepción)</span></td><td class="hl-ps">vit</td></tr>
              <tr><td>vouloir</td><td class="hl-ps">voulut</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="sec-label">AVOIR — paradigma completo</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">j'</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eut</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eûmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eûtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eurent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="grp23" data-idx="3">
        <div class="sec-label">Formas en -INT (VENIR, TENIR y derivados)</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="gram-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Pronombre</th><th>VENIR</th><th>TENIR</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>je</td><td class="hl-ps">vins</td><td class="hl-ps">tins</td></tr>
              <tr><td>tu</td><td class="hl-ps">vins</td><td class="hl-ps">tins</td></tr>
              <tr><td>il / elle</td><td class="hl-ps">vint</td><td class="hl-ps">tint</td></tr>
              <tr><td>nous</td><td class="hl-ps">vînmes</td><td class="hl-ps">tînmes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>vous</td><td class="hl-ps">vîntes</td><td class="hl-ps">tîntes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>ils / elles</td><td class="hl-ps">vinrent</td><td class="hl-ps">tinrent</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warn-box">
        <div class="warn-text">
          Los verbos derivados de VENIR y TENIR siguen el mismo patrón: <em>devenir → devint</em>, <em>revenir → revint</em>, <em>obtenir → obtint</em>, <em>retenir → retint</em>, <em>appartenir → appartint</em>.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- =================== SECTION 4 =================== -->
<section id="sec4" class="sec-block">
  <h2>4. Verbos irregulares</h2>

  <div class="gram-card">
    <div class="gram-card-body">
      <div class="def-box">
        Además de ÊTRE y AVOIR, varios verbos de alta frecuencia tienen passé simple con raíz propia que no puede deducirse del infinitivo. Imprescindibles para leer y reconocer texto literario.
      </div>

      <div class="chip-bar">
        <button class="chip active" onclick="selectChip('irr', 0, this)">ÊTRE / AVOIR</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('irr', 1, this)">FAIRE / ALLER</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('irr', 2, this)">Movimiento</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('irr', 3, this)">Percepción / voluntad</button>
        <button class="chip" onclick="selectChip('irr', 4, this)">Derivados</button>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel active" data-group="irr" data-idx="0">
        <div class="sec-label">ÊTRE</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">je</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fut</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fûmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fûtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">furent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="sec-label">AVOIR</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">j'</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eus</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eut</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eûmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eûtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">eurent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="note-box">
          <em>fut</em> y <em>eut</em> llevan acento circunflejo solo en <em>nous/vous</em> (<strong>fûmes, fûtes, eûmes, eûtes</strong>). La 3.ª persona singular no lo lleva: <em>il fut</em>, <em>il eut</em>.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="irr" data-idx="1">
        <div class="sec-label">FAIRE</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">je</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fis</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fis</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fit</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fîmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">fîtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">firent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="sec-label">ALLER</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="conj-table">
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">j'</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allai</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">tu</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allas</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">il / elle</td><td class="conj-form-ps">alla</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">nous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allâmes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">vous</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allâtes</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="conj-pron">ils / elles</td><td class="conj-form-ps">allèrent</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chip-panel" data-group="irr" data-idx="2">
        <div class="sec-label">Movimiento y cambio</div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="gram-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Infinitivo</th><th>3.ª sg.</th><th>3.ª pl.</th><th>Raíz PS</th></tr></thead>
